import React from 'react' import "./courses.css" import { coursesCard } from "../../dummydata" import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next' const CoursesCard = () => { const [t, i18n] = useTranslation("global"); return ( <>
{coursesCard.map((val) => (

{t(`Habout.${val.serviceName}`)}

{t(`Habout.${val.detail}`)}

From

${val.priceAll} / word

))}
) } export default CoursesCard
